custom_fields.default: Steps For Filling the Form: 1. Select Your Respective Departments Such as Arts, Commerce & Science. 2. Select the Program Grade. 3. To Select the Programs Click on the Add Row Button. 4. Select the programs in descending priority where first row will be highest and last row will be lowest. 5. Your can fill only Three(3) Programs according to your preferences. 6. Please Select Geography and Economics Program under Arts (Department) 7. You can only fill the Educational Details when you filled the Program Priority Table 8. Your Passport Photo size should not be more than 200 KB. 9. Don't Change Your Mobile No. and Email Id till Admission Gets Over. 10. After Saving the Applicant Form, you need to attach the required documents such as: Income Certificate, Caste Certificate, Resident Certificate, Etc. 11. After Submitting the Form, Please note down the Application Number and Print your Application Form for future reference. 12. After taking print of your Application Form, don't forget to Logout the page. 13. To Logout the page click on the top right Icon Button of your Application Form, then Click on Logout.
